HEADWORD: Haematosac
<hw>Haem"a*to*sac`</hw> <pr>(-s⟦acr⟧k`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Haemato-</ets> + <ets>sac</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>A vascular sac connected, beneath the brain, in many fishes, with
the infundibulum.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

